These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, almond-milk, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, cola-polo, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cola-polo##5
2. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is cola-polo##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person drinking almond-milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | milk   | cola    | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | weightlifting | parkour | cola-polo | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon, cabbage, peas
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
3. the person eating peas is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking juice is not the person eating watermelon##6
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice  | lemonade    | water | tea    |
| Food       | peas | watermelon | cabbage  | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, engineer, chef, analyst
1. the person drinking lemonade is not the firefighter##6
2. the engineer is not the person drinking coffee##6
3. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
4. the engineer is the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
8. the chef is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade       | almond-milk  | mirinda  | coffee |
| Job        | chef | analyst | engineer | firefighter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, frog, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, airplane, bike
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person driving the bike is not the owner of the turtle##6
4. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | turtle | frog | rabbit     | horse |
| Transport   | jet-ski     | airplane    | motorbike | bike    |

