.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, tea, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, skateboard, scooter, roller
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person driving the train is not the person drinking lemonade##6
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | sprite | tea | cola |
| Transport   | roller | train | skateboard     | scooter   |

