.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy, animation, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, mexican, nigerian
1. the japanese is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is not the argentine##6
3. the japanese is on the far right##1
4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the person watching animation movies is the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
7. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
8. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
9. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | animation    | time-travel  | epic   |
| Nationality   | mexican  | nigerian | argentine | japanese |

