.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, drama, mystery, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, jazz, trance, techno
1. the fan trance is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
2. the fan trance is not the person watching drama movies##6
3. the person watching romance movies is the fan jazz##1
4. the fan r&b is on the left or right of the fan techno##3
5. the fan trance is on the far left##1
6. the person watching drama movies is the fan r&b##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | drama     | mystery | romance |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b | techno      | jazz         |

