.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, coffee, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, videographer, writer, librarian
1. the nurse is on the left of the videographer##1
2. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the writer##5
3. the librarian is on the right of the videographer##1
4. the videographer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the videographer##3
6. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
8. the person drinking water is not the librarian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | water  | hot-chocolate        | coffee      | fanta          |
| Job        | nurse | videographer | librarian | writer |

