.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer, mechanic, accountant
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, ship, train, scooter
1. the nurse is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the ship is not the accountant##6
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
4. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the mechanic##1
7. the nurse is not the person driving the scooter##6
8. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | nurse  | mechanic | accountant    | freelancer |
| Transport   | ship | scooter | train | taxi  |

