.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, mouse, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, rugby, soccer
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the owner of the dog##6
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
6. the person who's sport is sailing is not the owner of the goat##6
7. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | mouse | dog        | goldfish  | goat     |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | soccer | sailing | rugby |

