.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, puzzles, dancing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, soul, punk
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
2. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
3. the fan soul is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the fan punk and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the fan house is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | dancing | puzzles    | reading | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | house | punk   | soul     |

