.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, zucchini, lime, pumpkin
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, taxi, subway
1. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
2. the person eating pumpkin is not the person driving the boat##6
3. the person driving the airplane is the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person driving the taxi is not the person eating pumpkin##6
6. the person eating zucchini is not the person driving the boat##6
7. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5
8. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | cauliflower  | lime | zucchini | pumpkin |
| Transport   | taxi | boat     | subway     | airplane    |

