.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, cauliflower, mango, broccoli
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific, martial-arts, crime
1. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
2. the person eating cauliflower is not the person watching scientific movies##6
3. the person eating watermelon is the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating cauliflower and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | broccoli | cauliflower      | watermelon | mango   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | martial-arts | crime   | documentary |

