2. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person watching drama movies is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk       | cola | mirinda     | juice     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie       | drama | scientific |

