4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the security-guard and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the security-guard is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
7. the software-developer is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
