The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, taxi, bus
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is not the person who's sport is cricket##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | cricket | climbing |
| Transport   | taxi   | snowmobile       | tram    | bus     |

