The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, water-polo, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person drinking 7up is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | coffee | cola | 7up         |
| Sport      | soccer | water-polo | tennis          | parkour |

