.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, baking
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, snake, frog
1. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the frog is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks | camping | baking |
| Pet     | snake  | dog      | turtle  | frog       |

