3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the tram is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | tea | milk | fanta      | sprite   |
| Transport   | airplane  | scooter   | bus | tram |

 